{
  "stem": "1895.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 493.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Always.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, on one of the jobs that I worked, there were Swiss people who were working in Auschwitz, in Birkenau, on a contract--",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To build a--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To build barracks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- a Swiss firm had bid on a contract to build barracks in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these were civil engineers that were sent by their firms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used the slave labor from Auschwitz to do their work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, don't tell me they didn't know what Auschwitz was about.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course they did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In 1944, none of this was a secret.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In '42, perhaps it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But not 1944.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I arrived, I was tattooed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "B-1477.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That makes me 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who were listening to concerts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the resentment stems primarily from the fact that we were made to watch the hangings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The hangings, to watch the hangings was just an awful ordeal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would chase us all out of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The barrack had to be clean.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If they caught anybody in the barrack, they would kill them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody had to go out and join the square to watch the hangings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would take like 20 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had the gallows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they would take one and put him on the gallows and hang him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the other one would not-- they wouldn't stop until he stopped twitching.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would take him off and take the next one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Or if they had three or four gallows, they would do it three or four at a time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the others were just waiting in line.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They're waiting their turn.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
